parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's occupants may not receive the necessary protection to prevent harm.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
resulting in injuries or fatalities to the vehicle's occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inconsistent airbag deployment can lead to injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's occupants may not receive the necessary protection to prevent harm.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unexpectedly or do not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
resulting in injuries or fatalities to the vehicle's occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper linkage can cause the wipers to stop working, reducing visibility while driving, especially in rainy or snowy conditions, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The windshield wipers stop working
the wiper arms separate from the wiper motor
the wiper linkages break or wear out
the wipers do not move smoothly
the wipers make a loud noise
the wipers leave streaks or residue on the windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper motor can cause the wipers to stop working, reducing visibility while driving, especially in rainy or snowy conditions, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The windshield wipers stop working
the wiper motor makes a loud noise
the wiper motor overheats
the wiper motor fails to turn on
the wiper motor slows down or speeds up unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield washer system can cause the washer fluid to leak into the passenger compartment, potentially causing health problems or discomfort for occupants.
symptoms: The windshield washer fluid leaks into the passenger compartment
the washer fluid has a strong
acrid smell
the washer nozzles clog or malfunction
the washer pump fails to turn on
the washer fluid reservoir overflows or leaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Spongy brake pedal
brake pedal feels soft
brake failure in emergency stopping situations
brakes require repeated replacement
brakes only last for a short period.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective windshield linkage can cause the windshield wipers to malfunction, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Windshield wipers do not work
linkage assembly needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The close proximity of the brake and gas pedals can cause the driver to accidentally press both pedals simultaneously, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Driver accidentally presses both brake and gas pedals at the same time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brakes to fail, leading to loss of control and accidents.
